  Headless, rootless, multi-architecture container image builder powered by Rootless BuildKit (buildkitd + buildctl). Provides a simple, Kaniko/Buildx-like CLI and an optional Kubernetes Job to build and push OCI images, with registry cache support and no long-running daemons.
